  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbe \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf - \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President will submit his resignation letter on reaching Singapore - Speaker informed",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Speaker party leader mentioned in the meeting that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa had mentioned to him that he would officially submit his letter of resignation after he left the Maldives for Singapore.",
        "In the party leaders' meeting held today under the chairmanship of the Speaker, the party leaders expressed their displeasure over the resignation of the President and the party leaders mentioned to the Speaker that if the people of the country continue to be deceived, it will have serious consequences.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe must step down as Acting President before President Gotabaya Rajapaksa officially announces his resignation.",
        "The party leaders have severely criticized that the people's struggle has intensified only after he was sworn in as the acting president.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa announced through Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe on the night of the 9th that following the intensification of the people's struggle, he would abide by the decision taken at the party leadership meeting.",
        "In the party leaders' meeting chaired by the Speaker, it was decided that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe should resign from their posts. The Speaker announced this decision to President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena said a couple of days ago that the President had told him that he would officially announce his resignation on the 13th.",
        "A special party leader meeting was held last Monday to examine the decisions to be taken following the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "It was decided that if the said president resigns, the parliament will be convened tomorrow, the nomination for the interim president will be considered next Tuesday, and the president will be elected through a secret ballot on the 20th.",
        "The Speaker mentioned to the media that the President has informed him that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has been elected as Acting President in accordance with the Constitution to carry out the duties of the President due to the fact that the President has left the country and that he will officially announce his resignation today (yesterday)."
      ],
